{"tid":1298242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭斯：美國將持續施壓　永不容許伊朗擁有核武","createTime":"2019-07-08T23:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T23:19:18.000Z","uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2540447c3594807e9cf09d15a40ad322b3cac21b","tid":1298242,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:16:38.000Z","msg":"美國副總統彭斯表示，美國會持續透過制裁向伊朗施壓，永遠不容許伊朗擁有核武，彭斯表示，美國和美軍準備好捍衛國家利益，並保護在中東地區的人員與公民，繼續反對伊朗惡勢力。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯在當地星期一，出席華府一個親以色列宗教團體的活動，傳媒發現，彭斯原定的發言稿，提及「美國不願意與伊朗開戰，並願意舉行談判」，不過，彭斯在演說中沒有提到這一說法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467322-20190709.htm&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjC2evTuabjAhVMAogKHa4ADCEQqQIIJygBMAA&amp;usg=AOvVaw2ASgovyb3o5-igs03xhMyF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467322-20190709.htm%26ved%3D0ahUKEwjC2evTuabjAhVMAogKHa4ADCEQqQIIJygBMAA%26usg%3DAOvVaw2ASgovyb3o5-igs03xhMyF&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=078d6cf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467322-20190709.htm%26ved%3D0ahUKEwjC2evTuabjAhVMAogKHa4ADCEQqQIIJygBMAA%26usg%3DAOvVaw2ASgovyb3o5-igs03xhMyF&h=6e47974e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467322-20190709.htm&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjC2evTuabjAhVMAogKHa4ADCEQqQIIJygBMAA&amp;usg=AOvVaw2ASgovyb3o5-igs03xhMyF</a>"},{"pid":"9df80644c54807fe70ba778468bc8cd0646869c2","tid":1298242,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:19:18.000Z","msg":"說好的六四演説呢？"}]}